## Strategy A (Test-and-Treat): Step-by-Step

### Chance node: Disease status



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
disease <- tibble(
  disease   = c(TRUE, FALSE),
  p_disease = c(p, 1 - p)
)

stopifnot(abs(sum(disease$p_disease) - 1) < 1e-10)

disease |> show_tbl("Chance node: disease status", "Rows sum to 1")
```

