### Expected values (Strategy B)



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
strat_B <- tree_B |>
  summarise(
    EV_cost = sum(path_prob * cost_total),
    EV_qaly = sum(path_prob * qaly),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) |>
  mutate(
    strategy = "Treat-All",
    NMB      = EV_qaly * lambda - EV_cost
  )

strat_B |> show_tbl("Expected values (Strategy B)", "E[Cost], E[QALY], and NMB")
```

